#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_acc_cash_flow
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_acc_cash_flow`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_acc_cash_flow` (
  `id` int(3) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=4 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

INSERT INTO `bpas_acc_cash_flow` (`id`, `name`) VALUES (1, 'Business Activities');
INSERT INTO `bpas_acc_cash_flow` (`id`, `name`) VALUES (2, 'Investing Activities');
INSERT INTO `bpas_acc_cash_flow` (`id`, `name`) VALUES (3, 'Financing Activities');

  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,

  `revenue_account` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `ar_account` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,

  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `id` (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=33 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_account_settings
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_account_settings`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_account_settings` (
  `id` int(1) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `biller_id` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `default_open_balance` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_sale` varchar(20) DEFAULT 'yes',
  `other_income` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_sale_discount` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_sale_tax` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_sale_freight` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_sale_deposit` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_receivable` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_purchase` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_purchase_discount` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_purchase_tax` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_purchase_freight` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_purchase_deposit` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_payable` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_stock` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_stock_adjust` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_cost` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_payroll` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_cash` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_credit_card` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_gift_card` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_cheque` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_loan` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_retained_earnings` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_cost_variant` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_interest_income` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_transfer_owner` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_tax_expense` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_vat_payable` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_salary_tax_payable` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_tax_duties_expense` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_salary_expense` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_salary_payable` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_product_tax` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_product_discount` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `accounting` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `payment_expense` tinyint(1) NOT NULL,
  `default_payment_pos` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_write_off` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pawn_stock_acc` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `installment_outstanding_acc` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_stock_using` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_expense` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_cost_adjustment` char(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `consignment_acc` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_stock_acc` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`,`biller_id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=4 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_account_transfer
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_account_transfer`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_account_transfer` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `charge_account` int(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `charge_amount` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_account` int(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_amount` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_amount2` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_amount3` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_amount4` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_account_transfer_item
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_account_transfer_item`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_account_transfer_item` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `transfer_account_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `paid_by` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `amount` decimal(10,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `charge_amount` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_amount` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_addon_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_addon_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_addon_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `item_code` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `price` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `description` varchar(200) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=3 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `bpas_addon_items` (`id`, `product_id`, `item_code`, `price`, `description`) VALUES (1, 1, 'm02', '1.0000', '');

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_addon_items_note
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_addon_items_note`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_addon_items_note` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `suspend_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `suspend_item_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `suspend_item_qty` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `item_number` varchar(200) NOT NULL,
  `addon_product_code` varchar(200) NOT NULL,
  `addon_product_qty` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `addon_status` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `row_id` varchar(200) NOT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_addresses
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_addresses`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_addresses` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `company_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `line1` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `line2` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `city` varchar(25) DEFAULT NULL,
  `postal_code` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `state` varchar(25) DEFAULT NULL,
  `country` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `contact_person` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `phone` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `noted` text,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `next_followup` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `kilometer` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `company_id` (`company_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=3 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `bpas_addresses` (`id`, `company_id`, `name`, `line1`, `line2`, `city`, `postal_code`, `state`, `country`, `contact_person`, `phone`, `noted`, `created_by`, `updated_at`, `next_followup`, `kilometer`, `status`) VALUES (1, 2, 'TK Round', 'Toul Kork', '', 'Phnom Penh', '', '', '', NULL, '0542834345', NULL, NULL, '2023-10-27 06:45:34', NULL, '12', 0);

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_adjustment_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_adjustment_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_adjustment_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `adjustment_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `type` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `adjustment_id` (`adjustment_id`),
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=6 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `bpas_adjustment_items` (`id`, `adjustment_id`, `product_id`, `option_id`, `quantity`, `warehouse_id`, `serial_no`, `type`, `expiry`) VALUES (1, 1, 14, NULL, '1.0000', 1, NULL, 'addition', NULL);

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_adjustments
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_adjustments`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_adjustments` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `note` text,
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `count_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,

  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `warehouse_id` (`warehouse_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=6 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_agreement
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_agreement`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_agreement` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `customer_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(55) NOT NULL,
  `biller` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `note` text,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `reference_no` varchar(45) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(125) NOT NULL,
  `unit_price` varchar(125) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` varchar(125) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_amount` varchar(125) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_term` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `delivery` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `account_no` text,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#

  `date_created` int(11) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=3 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_api_logs
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_api_logs`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_api_logs` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `uri` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `method` varchar(6) NOT NULL,
  `params` text,
  `api_key` varchar(40) NOT NULL,
  `ip_address` varchar(45) NOT NULL,
  `time` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `rtime` float DEFAULT NULL,
  `authorized` varchar(1) NOT NULL,
  `response_code` smallint(3) DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_approved
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_approved`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_approved` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `sale_order_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_request_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_order_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quote_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `approved_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `approved_status` varchar(25) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `approved_date` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `checked_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `checked_status` varchar(25) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `checked_date` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `rejected_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `rejected_status` varchar(25) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `rejected_date` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `delivery_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `delivery_status` varchar(25) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `delivery_date` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `unapproved_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unapproved_status` varchar(25) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `unapproved_date` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `preparation_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `preparation_status` varchar(25) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `preparation_date` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `issued_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `issued_status` varchar(25) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `issued_date` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `acknowledged_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `acknowledged_status` varchar(25) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `acknowledged_date` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `received_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `received_status` varchar(25) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `received_date` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `stock_received_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `stock_received_status` varchar(25) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `stock_received_date` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `quality_checked_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quality_checked_status` varchar(25) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `quality_checked_date` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `procurement_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `procurement_status` varchar(25) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `procurement_date` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `note` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `purchase_id` (`purchase_id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `purchase_id_2` (`purchase_id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `purchase_id_3` (`purchase_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=36 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_approved_by
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_approved_by`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_approved_by` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `group_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `form` varchar(100) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `approved_by` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `preparation_by` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `issued_by` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `acknowledged_by` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `received_by` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `stock_received_by` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `quality_checked_by` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `procurement_by` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=3 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `bpas_approved_by` (`id`, `group_id`, `form`, `approved_by`, `preparation_by`, `issued_by`, `acknowledged_by`, `received_by`, `stock_received_by`, `quality_checked_by`, `procurement_by`) VALUES (1, 13, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_asset_evaluation
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_asset_evaluation`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_asset_evaluation` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `expense_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `evaluation_date` date NOT NULL,
  `current_cost` decimal(11,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `accumulated` decimal(11,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_value` decimal(11,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `is_expense` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `dp_account` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `acc_account` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_att_attedances
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_att_attedances`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_att_attedances` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `employee_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `working_day` double DEFAULT '0',
  `present` double DEFAULT '0',
  `permission` double DEFAULT '0',
  `absent` double DEFAULT '0',
  `weekend_ot` double DEFAULT '0',
  `normal_ot` double DEFAULT '0',
  `holiday_ot` double DEFAULT '0',
  `late` double DEFAULT '0',
  `leave_early` double DEFAULT '0',
  `month` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `year` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `approve_att_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `employee_date` (`employee_id`,`date`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=7942 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_att_check_in_out`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_att_check_in_out` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `employee_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `check_time` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `check_time_int` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `device_id` int(3) DEFAULT NULL,

  KEY `id` (`employee_id`,`check_time_int`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=143 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_att_check_in_out_raw
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_att_check_in_out_raw`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_att_check_in_out_raw` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `finger_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `check_time` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `check_time_int` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `device_id` int(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pushed` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `id` (`finger_id`,`check_time_int`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_att_dailies
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_att_dailies`;

  `before_time` time DEFAULT NULL,
  `after_time` time DEFAULT NULL,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,

  KEY `id` (`employee_id`,`check_time`,`check_type`,`timeshift`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=440 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_attendance
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_attendance`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_attendance` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `status` enum('incomplete','pending','approved','rejected','deleted') COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL DEFAULT 'incomplete',
  `user_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `in_time` datetime NOT NULL,
  `out_time` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `checked_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` text COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci,
  `checked_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `reject_reason` text COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci,
  `deleted` int(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `user_id` (`user_id`),
  KEY `checked_by` (`checked_by`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_attendances
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_attendances`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_attendances` (
  `id` bigint(20) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `employee_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `user_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `shift_date` date NOT NULL,
  `shift_starttime` datetime NOT NULL,
  `shift_endtime` datetime NOT NULL,
  `shift_status` tinyint(4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0' COMMENT '1=checkin, 2=checkout',
  `shift_intype` tinyint(4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '0=qr, 1=remote',
  `shift_outtype` tinyint(4) DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '0=qr, 1=remote',
  `company_status` tinyint(4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1' COMMENT '0=pending, 1=Approved, 2=Rejected ',
  `shift_total_time` varchar(20) CHARACTER SET latin1 DEFAULT NULL COMMENT 'In minutes',
  `checkin_location` text CHARACTER SET latin1 COMMENT 'json data of (latitute, longitute)',
  `checkout_location` text CHARACTER SET latin1 COMMENT 'json data of (latitute, longitute)',
  `created_at` datetime NOT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `employee_id` (`employee_id`),
  KEY `user_id` (`user_id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

  `customer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `user_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tran_date` timestamp NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `description` text,
  `status` int(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `change_status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `print_index` int(11) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`audit_id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

  `item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,

  `price` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `qty` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `new_qty` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `type` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `user_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tran_date` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `description` text,
  `status` int(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `print_index` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `row_id` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=MyISAM DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_audit_booking
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_audit_booking`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_audit_booking` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `so_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `status` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `buy_status` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `customer_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `biller` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `staff_note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL,
  `product_discount` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `order_discount_id` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_discount` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `order_discount` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `product_tax` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `order_tax_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `total_tax` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `shipping` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `grand_total` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL,
  `sale_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_status` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_term` tinyint(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `term_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `due_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_items` smallint(6) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pos` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `paid` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `return_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `surcharge` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_sale_ref` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_sale_total` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `rounding` decimal(10,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `suspend_note` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `api` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `shop` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `address_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reserve_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `hash` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `manual_payment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cgst` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sgst` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `igst` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_method` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date_in` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `product_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `astatus` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `currency` varchar(50) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'usd',
  `status_booking` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `currency_rate_kh` decimal(11,3) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1.000',
  `currency_rate_bat` decimal(11,3) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1.000',
  `saleman_by` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `delivery_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `module_type` varchar(50) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'inventory',
  `is_loan` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `hide` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `number_customer` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `product_code` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_qty` int(2) DEFAULT '1',
  `original_price` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL,
  `expired_paid` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `zone_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `saleman_award_points` int(11) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_bom_items`;

  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `bom_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL,
  `cost` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `status` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `transfer_id` (`bom_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `option_id` (`option_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_chipmong
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_chipmong`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_chipmong` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` date NOT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `mallName` varchar(200) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `tenantName` varchar(200) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `grossSale` decimal(11,3) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.000',
  `taxAmount` decimal(11,3) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.000',
  `netSale` decimal(11,3) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.000',
  `cashAmountUsd` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cashAmountRiel` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `creditCardAmount` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `otherAmount` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `totalCreditCardTransaction` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `totalTransaction` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `depositAmountUsd` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `depositAmountRiel` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `exchangeRate` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `posId` varchar(50) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_id` varchar(200) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_date` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `push` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_commissions
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_commissions`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_commissions` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `amount` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL,
  `status` varchar(11) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL DEFAULT 'due',
  `note` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `percent` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `paid_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `paid_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `id` (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_companies
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_companies`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_companies` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `biller_id` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `group_id` int(10) unsigned DEFAULT NULL,
  `group_name` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `customer_group_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_group_name` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `parent_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `date2` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `code` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `name` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `company` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `contact_person` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `name_kh` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `company_kh` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `gender` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `age` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `vat_no` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `address` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `address_kh` varchar(300) NOT NULL,
  `city` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `state` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `postal_code` varchar(8) DEFAULT NULL,
  `country_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `country` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `phone` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `email` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf1` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf2` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf3` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf4` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf5` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cf6` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `invoice_footer` text,
  `payment_term` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `logo` varchar(255) DEFAULT 'logo.png',
  `award_points` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `credit_limit` decimal(11,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `find_consumer_comission` decimal(11,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `deposit_amount` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `deposit_amount_usd` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `deposit_amount_khr` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `deposit_amount_thb` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `price_group_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `price_group_name` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `gst_no` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `member_expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `source` varchar(200) DEFAULT NULL,
  `lead_convert` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `closed_date` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `lead_group` int(11) DEFAULT '1',
  `order_no` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `lead_color` int(11) DEFAULT '1',
  `end_date` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `save_point` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `zone_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `file` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `service_fee` decimal(11,3) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.000',
  `business_type` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `leader` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `village` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `commune` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `street_no` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `nssf` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `blood_group` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `service_package` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `nssf_number` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `paid_by` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `agent` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `student_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `products` varchar(300) DEFAULT NULL,
  `projects` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `working_day` double DEFAULT '0',
  `latitude` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `longitude` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `radius` int(11) DEFAULT '50' COMMENT 'radius in meters',
  `qr_code` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `group_id` (`group_id`),

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_con_absent_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_con_absent_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_con_absent_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `absent_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `officer_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `absent_date` date DEFAULT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_con_absents
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_con_absents`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_con_absents` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `project_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` text,
  `created_by` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` text
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_con_adjustment_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_con_adjustment_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_con_adjustment_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `adjustment_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `system_qty` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `machine_qty` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `different_qty` double DEFAULT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

  `id` int(11) NOT NULL,

  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` text,
  `from_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `to_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `commission_type` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_con_deliveries
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_con_deliveries`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_con_deliveries` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `customer_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `customer_code` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(5) NOT NULL,
  `biller` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `project_id` int(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `truck_id` int(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `truck_code` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `driver_id` int(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `driver_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `departure_time` time DEFAULT NULL,
  `arrival_time` time DEFAULT NULL,
  `finished_casting` time DEFAULT NULL,
  `seal_number` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `location_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `location_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `slump_id` int(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `slump_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `casting_type_id` int(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `casting_type_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `site_person` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `site_number` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `stregth_id` int(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `stregth_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pump_id` int(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pump_code` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pump_driver_id` int(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pump_driver_name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pump_move` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `status` varchar(50) DEFAULT 'pending',
  `sale_status` varchar(50) DEFAULT 'pending',
  `status_note` text,
  `gross_weight` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `truck_weight` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `weight_by` int(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `weight_status` varchar(10) DEFAULT 'pending',
  `driver_assistant` text,
  `kilometer` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `markup_qty` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `operator_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `group_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_cost` double DEFAULT NULL
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_consignment_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_consignment_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_consignment_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `consignment_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `consignment_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `product_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_price` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_unit_price` double NOT NULL,
  `unit_price` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` double NOT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` double NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` double NOT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `comment` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `return_qty` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_qty` double DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `quote_id` (`consignment_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_consignments
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_consignments`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_consignments` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `consignment_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `customer_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `biller` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total` double NOT NULL,
  `grand_total` double NOT NULL,
  `status` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `valid_day` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `id` (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_costing
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_costing`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_costing` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_item_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `purchase_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `service_cost` decimal(11,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_net_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `purchase_unit_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_net_unit_price` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `sale_unit_price` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) NOT NULL,
  `quantity_balance` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `inventory` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `overselling` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `hide` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_coupon
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_coupon`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_coupon` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `card_no` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `value` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `used` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `customer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `card_no` (`card_no`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_credit_note
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_credit_note`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_credit_note` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `sale_reference_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `address` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(15) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_credit_note_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_credit_note_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_credit_note_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `credit_note_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `product_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_unit_price` double NOT NULL,
  `unit_price` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` double NOT NULL,
  `quantity` double NOT NULL,
  `real_quantity` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_tax` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_discount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` double NOT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_price` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `width` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `height` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `square` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `square_qty` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `foc_qty` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `description` text,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `quote_id` (`credit_note_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_customer_groups
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_customer_groups`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_customer_groups` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `percent` int(11) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=6 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `bpas_customer_groups` (`id`, `name`, `percent`) VALUES (1, 'General', 0);
INSERT INTO `bpas_customer_groups` (`id`, `name`, `percent`) VALUES (2, 'Discount 10%', -10);
INSERT INTO `bpas_customer_groups` (`id`, `name`, `percent`) VALUES (3, 'Distributor', -15);
INSERT INTO `bpas_customer_groups` (`id`, `name`, `percent`) VALUES (4, 'New Customer (+10)', 10);
INSERT INTO `bpas_customer_groups` (`id`, `name`, `percent`) VALUES (5, '25%', -25);


#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_customer_package
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_customer_package`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_customer_package` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `code` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(250) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `period` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `period_type` varchar(55) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL,
  `price` decimal(11,3) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.000',
  `description` text CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_customer_stock_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_customer_stock_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_customer_stock_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `customer_stock_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `product_unit_code` varchar(10) DEFAULT '0',
  `unit_quantity` double DEFAULT '0',
  `serial_no` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `customer_stock_id` (`customer_stock_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_customer_stocks
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_customer_stocks`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_customer_stocks` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `table_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `note` text,
  `created_by` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `returned_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `returned_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfered_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `transfered_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(10) DEFAULT 'pending',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `warehouse_id` (`warehouse_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `customer_id` (`customer_id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_customer_trucks
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_customer_trucks`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_customer_trucks` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `customer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `name` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `plate_number` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_date_format
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_date_format`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_date_format` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `js` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `php` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `sql` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=7 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `bpas_date_format` (`id`, `js`, `php`, `sql`) VALUES (4, 'dd-mm-yyyy', 'd-m-Y', '%d-%m-%Y');
INSERT INTO `bpas_date_format` (`id`, `js`, `php`, `sql`) VALUES (5, 'dd/mm/yyyy', 'd/m/Y', '%d/%m/%Y');
INSERT INTO `bpas_date_format` (`id`, `js`, `php`, `sql`) VALUES (6, 'dd.mm.yyyy', 'd.m.Y', '%d.%m.%Y');


#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_deliveries
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_deliveries`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_deliveries` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `biller` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `clear_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_order_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `do_reference_no` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `sale_reference_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `so_reference_no` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `clear_reference_no` varchar(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `customer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `address` varchar(1000) NOT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `clear_note` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `clear_created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(15) DEFAULT NULL,
  `paid_by` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `delivered_by` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `received_by` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `money_collection` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `collection_amount` decimal(11,3) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.000',
  `clear_amount` decimal(11,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `balance` decimal(11,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `send_number` int(25) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=3 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_delivery_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_delivery_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_delivery_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `delivery_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `parent_id` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `product_code` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `product_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `option_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `real_unit_price` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_unit_price` double NOT NULL,
  `unit_price` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `unit_quantity` double NOT NULL,
  `quantity` double NOT NULL,
  `real_quantity` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_tax` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `discount` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `item_discount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `subtotal` double NOT NULL,
  `serial_no` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_unit_code` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `width` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `height` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `square` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `square_qty` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `foc_qty` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_order_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `quote_id` (`delivery_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=4 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_deposits
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_deposits`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_deposits` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `company_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `amount` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `amount_usd` decimal(11,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `amount_khr` decimal(11,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `amount_thb` decimal(11,4) DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `paid_by` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `account_code` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `bank_code` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `po_reference_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `so_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `po_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `deposit_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `opening` tinyint(1) unsigned zerofill NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `attachment` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `id` (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `company_id` (`company_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `created_by` (`created_by`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `updated_by` (`updated_by`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `account_code` (`account_code`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `bank_code` (`bank_code`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `payment_id` (`payment_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `deposit_id` (`deposit_id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=3 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

  `id` int(10) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,

  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `authorize_id` int(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `employee_id` int(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `plan_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `address_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `account` int(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` text CHARACTER SET utf8mb4,
  `create_by` int(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 DEFAULT NULL,
  `type` varchar(25) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `using_reference_no` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_using_cost` decimal(25,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `shop` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `id` (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `warehouse_id` (`warehouse_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `authorize_id` (`authorize_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `employee_id` (`employee_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `customer_id` (`customer_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `plan_id` (`plan_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `address_id` (`address_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `create_by` (`create_by`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `reference_no` (`reference_no`(191)) USING BTREE,
  KEY `using_reference_no` (`using_reference_no`(191)) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_expenses
#

  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,

  `paid_by` char(50) DEFAULT NULL,

  `order_discount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_discount_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `order_tax_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `paid` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_status` char(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` char(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_expenses_budget
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_expenses_budget`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_expenses_budget` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `reference` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `amount_usd` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `amount_khm` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `amount` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `category_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `budget_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `bank_account` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `bank_code` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_expenses_customer
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_expenses_customer`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_expenses_customer` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `reference` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `currency` varchar(50) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'USD',
  `amount` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `category_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `budget_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `bank_account` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `bank_code` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,

  `amount` decimal(15,2) NOT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `card_id` (`card_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_gift_cards
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_gift_cards`;

  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `card_no` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `value` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL,
  `discount` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `balance` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `card_no` (`card_no`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_gl_charts
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_gl_charts`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_gl_charts` (
  `accountcode` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `accountname` varchar(200) DEFAULT '',
  `parent_acc` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `sectionid` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `account_tax_id` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `acc_level` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `lineage` varchar(500) NOT NULL,
  `bank` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `value` decimal(55,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `type` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `inactive` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `parent_code` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cash_flow` tinyint(3) DEFAULT '0',
  `nature` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`accountcode`) USING BTREE,
  UNIQUE KEY `accountcode_2` (`accountcode`),
  KEY `AccountCode` (`accountcode`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `AccountName` (`accountname`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `parent_acc` (`parent_acc`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `sectionid` (`sectionid`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `account_tax_id` (`account_tax_id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

INSERT INTO `bpas_gl_charts` (`accountcode`, `accountname`, `parent_acc`, `sectionid`, `account_tax_id`, `acc_level`, `lineage`, `bank`, `value`, `type`, `inactive`, `parent_code`, `cash_flow`, `nature`) VALUES (100100, 'Cash', 0, 10, 0, 0, '', 1, '0.00', 0, 0, NULL, 0, NULL);

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_gl_sections
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_gl_sections`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_gl_sections` (
  `sectionid` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `code` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sectionname` text,
  `sectionname_kh` text,
  `AccountType` char(2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `description` text,
  `nature` int(11) DEFAULT '1',
  `order_stat` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`sectionid`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `sectionid` (`sectionid`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

INSERT INTO `bpas_gl_sections` (`sectionid`, `code`, `sectionname`, `sectionname_kh`, `AccountType`, `description`, `nature`, `order_stat`) VALUES (10, 'AS', 'CURRENT ASSETS', 'ទ្រព្យសកម្មរយះពេលខ្លី', 'AS', 'CURRENT ASSETS', 1, 10);

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_gl_trans
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_gl_trans`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_gl_trans` (
  `tran_id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `tran_type` varchar(20) DEFAULT '0',
  `tran_no` bigint(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `tran_date` datetime DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `sectionid` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `account_code` int(19) DEFAULT '0',
  `narrative` varchar(100) DEFAULT '',
  `amount` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `reference_no` varchar(55) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  `note` text,
  `description` varchar(250) DEFAULT '',
  `biller_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `bank` tinyint(3) DEFAULT '0',
  `gov_tax` tinyint(3) DEFAULT '0',
  `reference_gov_tax` varchar(55) DEFAULT '',
  `people_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `invoice_ref` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `ref_type` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_name` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_type` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `people` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `type` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status_tax` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `supplier_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payroll_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `hide` int(2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `expense_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `depreciation_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reconciled` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `activity_type` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`tran_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `Account` (`account_code`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `TranDate` (`tran_date`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `TypeNo` (`tran_no`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `Type_and_Number` (`tran_type`,`tran_no`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `tran_id` (`tran_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `sectionid` (`sectionid`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `reference_no` (`reference_no`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `created_by` (`created_by`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `updated_by` (`updated_by`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `customer_id` (`customer_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `payment_id` (`payment_id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=182 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_groups
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_groups`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_groups` (
  `id` mediumint(8) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(20) NOT NULL,
  `description` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=16 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `bpas_groups` (`id`, `name`, `description`, `status`) VALUES (1, 'owner', 'Owner', 1);
INSERT INTO `bpas_groups` (`id`, `name`, `description`, `status`) VALUES (2, 'admin', 'Administrator', 1);
INSERT INTO `bpas_groups` (`id`, `name`, `description`, `status`) VALUES (3, 'branch', 'Manager', 1);
INSERT INTO `bpas_groups` (`id`, `name`, `description`, `status`) VALUES (4, 'customer', 'Customer', 1);
INSERT INTO `bpas_groups` (`id`, `name`, `description`, `status`) VALUES (5, 'supplier', 'Supplier', 1);
INSERT INTO `bpas_groups` (`id`, `name`, `description`, `status`) VALUES (6, 'salesman', 'Saleman', 1);
INSERT INTO `bpas_groups` (`id`, `name`, `description`, `status`) VALUES (8, 'employee', 'Employee', 1);
INSERT INTO `bpas_groups` (`id`, `name`, `description`, `status`) VALUES (13, 'audit', 'Tax Auditor', 1);
INSERT INTO `bpas_groups` (`id`, `name`, `description`, `status`) VALUES (14, 'account', 'Accounting', 1);
INSERT INTO `bpas_groups` (`id`, `name`, `description`, `status`) VALUES (15, 'sm', 'Sale Manager', 1);


#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_hr_award
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_hr_award`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_hr_award` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `award_type` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `award_month` char(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` text,
  `status` char(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `position_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `department_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `group_id` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `gift` varchar(200) DEFAULT NULL,
  `cash` varchar(200) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=5 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

INSERT INTO `bpas_hr_award` (`id`, `award_type`, `date`, `award_month`, `biller_id`, `attachment`, `created_by`, `created_at`, `note`, `status`, `updated_by`, `updated_at`, `position_id`, `department_id`, `group_id`, `gift`, `cash`) VALUES (4, 131, '2022-07-07 18:15:00', '07/2022', 3, NULL, 1, '2023-05-10 15:43:05', NULL, 'pending', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, 'iphone', '');


#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_hr_award_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_hr_award_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_hr_award_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `award_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `employee_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=16 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

INSERT INTO `bpas_hr_award_items` (`id`, `award_id`, `employee_id`) VALUES (15, 4, 1);

  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_hr_employees
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_hr_employees`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_hr_employees` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `finger_id` varchar(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `nric_no` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `empcode` varchar(225) DEFAULT '0',
  `candidate` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `candidate_status` varchar(25) DEFAULT 'employee' COMMENT '1:candidate,2:shortlist,3:interview,0;employee',
  `firstname` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `lastname` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `firstname_kh` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `lastname_kh` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `photo` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `dob` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `gender` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `phone` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `email` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `address` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `nationality` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `marital_status` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `non_resident` bigint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  `nssf` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `nssf_number` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` text,
  `book_type` char(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `work_permit_number` char(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `workbook_number` char(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `type` char(50) DEFAULT 'Staff',
  `pob` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_hr_employees_working_info
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_hr_employees_working_info`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_hr_employees_working_info` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `employee_id` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `department_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `group_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `position_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `policy_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `roster` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `employee_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `employee_type_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `resigned_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_method` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `net_salary` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `currency` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `self_tax` bigint(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `salary_tax` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `absent_rate` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `permission_rate` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tax_rate` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `monthly_rate` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `late_early_rate` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `normal_ot_rate` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `holiday_ot_rate` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `weekend_ot_rate` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `kpi_type` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `additions` text,
  `deductions` text,
  `annual_leave` double DEFAULT '0',
  `monthly_annual_leave` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `special_leave` double DEFAULT '0',
  `sick_leave` double DEFAULT '0',
  `other_leave` double DEFAULT '0',
  `seniority` double NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `no_seniority` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attendance_bonus` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `special_bonus` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `tra_acc_allowance` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `union` decimal(11,3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pension` tinyint(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_type` char(50) DEFAULT 'monthly',
  `salary_two_time` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `employee_id` (`employee_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `policy_id` (`policy_id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=16 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

  `description` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_hr_kpi
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_hr_kpi`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_hr_kpi` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `month` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `employee_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `kpi_type` int(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `result` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `measure` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `measure_kh` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `measure_color` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `manager_note` text,
  `employee_note` text,
  `attachment` text,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_installments
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_installments`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_installments` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `biller` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `sale_item_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `project_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `description` text,
  `price` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `installment_amount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `deposit` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_rate` varchar(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_period` int(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_method` int(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `principal_amount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `currency` char(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'USD',
  `term` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `frequency_id` int(3) DEFAULT NULL,
  `frequency` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `penalty_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(10) DEFAULT 'active',
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `id` (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `sale_id` (`sale_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `status` (`status`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

INSERT INTO `bpas_installments` (`id`, `biller_id`, `biller`, `reference_no`, `sale_id`, `sale_item_id`, `product_id`, `project_id`, `warehouse_id`, `customer_id`, `customer`, `description`, `price`, `installment_amount`, `deposit`, `interest_rate`, `interest_period`, `interest_method`, `principal_amount`, `currency`, `term`, `frequency_id`, `frequency`, `payment_date`, `penalty_id`, `status`, `created_by`, `created_date`, `updated_by`, `updated_at`) VALUES (1, 3, 'SBC Solution/Kimpheng', '24/0001', 8, NULL, NULL, NULL, 7, 156, 'Market ABC', 'Computer ', '300', '300', '0', '0', 0, 1, '300', 'USD', 6, 4, 30, '2024-03-21', 1, 'active', 1, '2024-02-21 22:06:00', NULL, NULL);

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_inventory_valuation_details
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_inventory_valuation_details`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_inventory_valuation_details` (
  `id` bigint(20) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `biller_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `product_code` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `product_name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `category_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `sub_category_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `warehouse_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `type` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `name` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `quantity` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `cost` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `qty_on_hand` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `avg_cost` decimal(15,4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `plan_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `field_id` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `id` (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `product_id` (`product_id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `category_id` (`category_id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_leads
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_leads`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_leads` (
  `task_id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `company` text NOT NULL,
  `closed_date` timestamp NULL DEFAULT NULL,
  `lead_group` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `lead_order` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `lead_color` varchar(20) DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`task_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_loan_applications
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_loan_applications`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_loan_applications` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `biller` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `borrower_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `borrower` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `principal_amount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `currency` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  `interest_rate` varchar(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_period` int(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_method` int(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `insurance_rate` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `grace_interest_charge` int(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `term` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `frequency` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `loan_product_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `borrower_type_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `loan_officer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `teller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(10) DEFAULT 'active',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=18 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_loan_borrowers
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_loan_borrowers`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_loan_borrowers` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `application_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unique_type_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `unique_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `code` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `type` varchar(50) DEFAULT 'Customer',
  `first_name` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `last_name` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `gender` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `phone` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL,
  `email` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `dob` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `marital_status` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `working_status` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `country_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `province_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `district_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `commune_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `village_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,

  `home_no` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `address` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `longitude` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `latitude` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `photo` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` text,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(10) DEFAULT 'active',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=17 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_loan_items
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_loan_items`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_loan_items` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `loan_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `deadline` date NOT NULL,
  `period` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `payment` double NOT NULL,
  `principal` double NOT NULL,
  `interest` double NOT NULL,
  `penalty` double DEFAULT '0',
  `fee_charge` double DEFAULT '0',
  `balance` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `paid` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `status` varchar(100) DEFAULT 'pending',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `id` (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_loan_payment
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_loan_payment`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_loan_payment` (
  `loan_id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `user_id` tinyint(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_id` tinyint(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_id` tinyint(11) NOT NULL,
  `reference` varchar(155) NOT NULL,
  `no` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `day` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `pay_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `monthly_payment` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `principal` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_rate` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL,
  `interest` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,

  PRIMARY KEY (`loan_id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=333 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_loan_products
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_loan_products`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_loan_products` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `principal_amount_default` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `principal_amount_min` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `principal_amount_max` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_rate_default` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_rate_min` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_rate_max` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `term_default` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `term_min` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `term_max` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `frequency` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `currency` varchar(55) DEFAULT 'USD',
  `interest_method` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_period` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `grace_interest_charge` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `late_repayment_penalty_recurring` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `late_repayment_penalty_calculate` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `late_repayment_penalty_amount` double(11,0) DEFAULT NULL,
  `late_repayment_penalty_period` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `charge_ids` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `default_bank_account` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `loan_portfolio_account` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_receivable_account` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_income_account` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `penalty_income_account` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=6 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

INSERT INTO `bpas_loan_products` (`id`, `name`, `principal_amount_default`, `principal_amount_min`, `principal_amount_max`, `interest_rate_default`, `interest_rate_min`, `interest_rate_max`, `term_default`, `term_min`, `term_max`, `frequency`, `currency`, `interest_method`, `interest_period`, `grace_interest_charge`, `late_repayment_penalty_recurring`, `late_repayment_penalty_calculate`, `late_repayment_penalty_amount`, `late_repayment_penalty_period`, `charge_ids`, `default_bank_account`, `loan_portfolio_account`, `interest_receivable_account`, `interest_income_account`, `penalty_income_account`) VALUES (1, 'Under 20,000$', '10000', '500', '20000', '0.5', '0.2', '10', 50, 10, 100, 1, 'USD', 3, 4, 0, 1, 3, '1', 0, '[\"0\"]', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_loan_reschedule
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_loan_reschedule`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_loan_reschedule` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `user_id` tinyint(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer_id` tinyint(5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_id` tinyint(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference` varchar(155) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_method` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `outstanding_balance` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `disburse_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `first_payment_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `disburse_amount` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `total_interest` decimal(13,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `deposit_amount` decimal(25,2) DEFAULT '0.00',
  `term` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_rate` float(12,0) DEFAULT NULL,
  `principle_nego` decimal(13,2) DEFAULT NULL,
  `term_nego` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_rate_nego` float(12,0) DEFAULT NULL,
  `register_date` timestamp NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `warehouse_id` int(5) DEFAULT '0',
  `percent` varchar(50) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_term` varchar(225) DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(25) DEFAULT 'pending',
  `reschedule_time` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` text,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=MyISAM AUTO_INCREMENT=28 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_loans
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_loans`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_loans` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `application_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `biller_id` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  `biller` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `borrower_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `borrower` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `principal_amount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `currency` varchar(255) DEFAULT 'USD',
  `interest_rate` varchar(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `insurance_rate` decimal(25,2) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.00',
  `interest_period` int(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `interest_method` int(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `grace_interest_charge` int(4) DEFAULT NULL,
  `term` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `frequency` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `payment_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `loan_product_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `borrower_type_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `loan_officer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `teller_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `disburse_amount` double DEFAULT NULL,
  `fee_charge_amount` decimal(25,4) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0.0000',
  `disbursed_at` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `disbursed_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_by` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `updated_at` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` varchar(10) DEFAULT 'active',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  KEY `id` (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

#
# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_locations
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_locations`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_locations` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` varchar(100) DEFAULT NULL,
  `type` varchar(10) DEFAULT NULL,
  `parent_id` int(11) DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 ROW_FORMAT=COMPACT;

  `login` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `time` int(11) unsigned DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=33 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_maintenance
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_maintenance`;

CREATE TABLE `bpas_maintenance` (
  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `date` timestamp NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `sale_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `amount` double NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `payment` double NOT NULL DEFAULT '0',
  `customer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `reference_no` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `maintenance_date` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `created_by` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `attachment` varchar(55) DEFAULT NULL,
  `note` varchar(1000) DEFAULT NULL,
  `maintenance_status` varchar(20) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'pending',
  `frequency` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `term` tinyint(5) DEFAULT '0',
  `status` tinyint(1) DEFAULT '0',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

  `discount` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `customer_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `customer` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  `expiry` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `created_by` varchar(55) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  UNIQUE KEY `card_no` (`card_no`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

# TABLE STRUCTURE FOR: bpas_module_user
#

DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `bpas_module_user`;

  `id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `user_id` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `allow_using_user` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `plan_id` int(11) DEFAULT '1',
  `subscribe_id` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `duration` int(10) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1' COMMENT 'month',
  `branch_id` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `modules` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `website_url` varchar(250) DEFAULT NULL,
  `register_date` datetime NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `start_using_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `expired_date` date DEFAULT NULL,
  `status` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '1',
  `suspend_date` datetime DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
